{"tid":147990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔超突發〕金正男之子現身YOUTUBE感謝美國","createTime":"2017-03-08T09:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T00:18:01.000Z","uid":30561,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f8d89d27120f52f93fa0e870a5bcb892efc4a8a","tid":147990,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:06:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7FCqioXAbXI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7FCqioXAbXI&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6ce9729d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7FCqioXAbXI</a><br />\n<br />\n北韓領導人金正恩大哥金正男在馬來西亞遇刺身亡，一段金正男兒子金韓松的影片，今日在YouTube上流傳。金韓松的影片長度約為40秒，而他以英文講述，並表示「我爸被殺害了」。 <br />\n<br />\n影片一開始金韓松說「我是金韓松，來自北韓的金氏家族」，隨後他出示自己的護照。《韓聯社》表示，金韓松拿的應該是北韓外交人員所使用的護照。金韓松隨後說：「我爸在幾天前被殺害了。」他也說，現在他和母親以及妹妹在一起，並感謝第三人協助，影片最後他還露出淺淺的微笑。 <br />\n<br />\n《韓聯社》報導也指出，金韓松家族現在正由一個民間集團「千里馬民間防衛」所保護，該組織宣稱保護金韓松家族的安全，並感謝荷蘭、中國與美國的協助，另外也感謝一個「無名」國家。不過南韓統一部官員指出，並沒有聽說過「千里馬民防」這個組織。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保護金正男家人的秘密組織：「千里馬民防」 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/MPNvmq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FMPNvmq.png&h=97407eaa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一名自稱是金正男兒子金韓松的男子在神秘組織「千里馬民防」協助下，拍攝一段YouTube影片向外界報平安。根據報導，金正男家人於上月向該組織求救，目前已被安置在不明地點。 <br />\n<br />\n影片中右上方可見「千里馬民防」（Cheollima Civil Defense）字眼，根據馬來西亞《東方日報》引述該組織網站聲明，金正男的家屬上個月向他們求救，要求組織協助逃離並提供保護，「他們一家3口迅速被護送至安全的地點。」該組織感謝4國協助保護金正男的家屬，包括荷蘭、中國、美國和第4個不願具名的政府。 <br />\n<br />\n報導指出，馬來西亞警方接受詢問時表示，從未聽過該組織，但強調警方有方法聯繫金正男的家屬。 <br />\n另據馬來西亞《中國報》報導，「千里馬民防」組織的名稱與北韓歷史關係深厚。「千里馬運動」是北韓前領導人金日成於1957年至1961年發展5年計劃的名稱。此運動的發端是金日成1956年訪問降仙製鋼廠，指示要以千里馬的精神生產鋼材，之後該廠改名千里馬製鋼聯合企業所。1960年平壤市造了千里馬銅像以紀念此事。 <br />\n<br />\n後來，「千里馬運動」成為北韓象徵，並稱此時代為「千里馬時代」。1961年4月15日在平壤市萬壽台崗上建立了象徵千里馬運動的「千里馬銅像」。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\noh 越來越有趣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb5a964e75e6d07028e59b06daedb89143678b9","tid":147990,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=al8Y0hcjRsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dal8Y0hcjRsc&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c378e26d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=al8Y0hcjRsc</a>"},{"pid":"e05388e6439dc3a52144ccd24731267e2bb16504","tid":147990,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:08:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5qyv8dT2q0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5qyv8dT2q0w&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=167948eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5qyv8dT2q0w</a>"},{"pid":"bda630abcc1d1630d5abbeb8866ef534ebdf40c2","tid":147990,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:08:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_v_fxsoFSt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_v_fxsoFSt4&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0cd1ac0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_v_fxsoFSt4</a>"},{"pid":"817817a34c787f00404843651b9ec1df3746174c","tid":147990,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ntTY1T5b9K8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DntTY1T5b9K8&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0a78a163\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ntTY1T5b9K8</a>"},{"pid":"716066731ee99fae606509a00a353b55b2324c7a","tid":147990,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"「千里馬民防」（Cheollima Civil Defense）<br />\n草泥馬民防<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bd2c225cf91fc8fa46d98c961db7323631d157","tid":147990,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"感謝中國同美國? 案情唔簡單!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb250dc26f78a719fe42f081d91e49301022847","tid":147990,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:24:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得，金正恩死期不遠<br />\n最近太多關於北韓既野，會有太多巧合"},{"pid":"62de049459f981096c9fe8bd9df058264cad4ea4","tid":147990,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:29:36.000Z","msg":"（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"71a83923e7abeb7e28b32bf94cc00fa8dd4ed154","tid":147990,"uid":1884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:34:46.000Z","msg":"幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82629d52536982b77554f9c37292868f340022e","tid":147990,"uid":18564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:36:28.000Z","msg":"即係金正男全家仲有班老臣子跟住佢護駕<br />\n但金正恩又收買唔到班老野勢力又隊佢地唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e4b698547e06a4a9f9b2fcbb65396ff9914442","tid":147990,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得，金正恩死期不遠<br />\n最近太多關於北韓既野，會有太多巧合</blockquote><br />\n雜種頂佢唔順 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a408d2ce92c13912f1b60786b0f09dd84efa48","tid":147990,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"南北韓終於要統一"},{"pid":"13f9647c758e4246872fd3e9b8de1f7b61108c06","tid":147990,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:43:37.000Z","msg":"佢識講流利廣東話"},{"pid":"f7fad5b7f8abb31d873876d0a665bacca969775b","ti